      "amount": "2 tbsp"
    },
    {
      "name": "vegetable stock",
      "amount": "2 cups"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a cataplana over medium heat until shimmering.",
    "Add lemongrass paste, turmeric, cumin, and coriander and sauté until fragrant about 2 minutes.",
    "Stir in sliced carrot and bell pepper and cook for 3 minutes until slightly softened.",
    "Add the cabbage leaves and napa cabbage, deglaze with a splash of tamari, and cover; cook for 5 minutes until greens begin to wilt.",
    "Pour in vegetable stock, coconut milk, and sliced nuka-pickle and bring to a gentle simmer.",
    "Reduce heat to low, cover, and simmer for 15 minutes until all vegetables are tender and flavors meld.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with a squeeze of fresh lime if desired."
  ],
